WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.680 --> 00:00:01.760
The Barclays app

2
00:00:02.160 --> 00:00:06.520
How to use the Barclays app to
identify yourself when shopping online

3
00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:10.480
If you're shopping online,

4
00:00:10.640 --> 00:00:13.920
you may be asked to identify
yourself when making a payment.

5
00:00:15.120 --> 00:00:17.480
Don't worry, it's simple to do.

6
00:00:17.800 --> 00:00:20.400
Let us show you how you can use
your Barclays app

7
00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:22.880
to confirm that it's
you making the payment.

8
00:00:23.360 --> 00:00:25.240
After you've added your card details,

9
00:00:25.440 --> 00:00:29.160
select ‘use the Barclays app
from the drop-down menu,

10
00:00:29.880 --> 00:00:31.520
then tap ‘Next’.

11
00:00:32.040 --> 00:00:36.440
If you have push notifications enabled
you will receive an alert from us.

12
00:00:37.120 --> 00:00:41.880
If you don't, watch our video on how to
switch on push notifications.

13
00:00:42.440 --> 00:00:45.080
Tap on the alert to open the Barclays app,

14
00:00:45.600 --> 00:00:48.160
which you'll need to log
into in the usual way.

15
00:00:48.720 --> 00:00:50.880
Then simply tap to confirm

16
00:00:51.240 --> 00:00:53.680
and your transaction will be complete.

